{"tid":619942,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"福岡8日7夜行程","createTime":"2018-04-07T06:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T08:18:28.000Z","uid":130662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8e62297d35052102a4dd0f67b8b0c640311229","tid":619942,"uid":130662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:44:02.000Z","msg":"黎緊5月中買左機票去福岡，上網睇左D遊記諗住咁樣玩<br />\n<br />\nDay1: 中午12點到福岡，落機後係博多附近行下hea下，櫛田神社，中州屋台<br />\n<br />\nDay2: 太宰府天滿宮，九州國立博物館，柳川<br />\n<br />\nDay3: JR入長崎，原爆館，眼鏡橋，稻佐山<br />\n<br />\nDay4: 豪斯登堡，夜晚返天神<br />\n<br />\nDay5: 門司港，下關， 鐵道博物館，小倉<br />\n<br />\nDay6: 海之中道海濱公園，大濠公園，福岡塔，天神地下街<br />\n<br />\nDay7: 能古島，Marina outlet，博多運河城<br />\n<br />\nDay8: 中午機返香港<br />\n<br />\n北九3 Day Pass同5 Day Pass價錢差唔遠，應該會買5 Day Pass，係咪應該Day2 - 6用張Pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打幫手比D意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b326faae1b45e6f2b3532918ace1f7459cb8c982","tid":619942,"uid":11003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"運河城 你第一日可以去埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e19742b808f07f42bb041acc19f26a19b3590b","tid":619942,"uid":130662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"唔記得講除左第3日會係長崎book多晚酒店其他全部住天神"},{"pid":"d3f0c8ffc42ea2791e19df9909ad7c73011a8237","tid":619942,"uid":130662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b326faae1b45e6f2b3532918ace1f7459cb8c982","tid":619942,"uid":11003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"運河城 你第一日可以去埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"諗住最後一日先去買野買手信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f19c44503cab7f78b753d267bb3605c57e0ad2b","tid":619942,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep